Title: Establishes the hours during which alcoholic beverages may be sold on certain international airport property
Summary: Establishes the hours during which alcoholic beverages may be sold on certain international airport property; authorizes the sale of alcohol from 6:00 AM to 3:00 AM.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the alcoholic beverage control law, in relation to establishing the hours during which alcoholic beverages may be sold on certain international airport property
